<title>USA: AMEX closing averages.</title>
<headline>AMEX closing averages.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed higher in light trading on Monday.</p>
<p>The Amex Composite index closed at 587.48, up 0.76.</p>
<p>The average price per share rose 2 cents.</p>
<p>Advances beat declines 256 to 243.</p>
<p>Preliminary volume was 14,020,685 compared with 21,029,530 on Friday.</p>
<p>(Prices official as of 1630 EST/2130 GMT)</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1881))</p>
